The paper deals with developing an efficient online algorithm for robust principal component analysis and applies it to real-time background subtraction of surveillance video. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CV), statistics (cs.ST), information theory (cs.IT), and numerical analysis (cs.NA).
